<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CNow is the time for us to pull the fu=
ture forward by aggressively addressing our legacy leases and dramatically =
improving our balance sheet,=E2=80=9D Tolley continued.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Not that long ago, if the chief executive offi=
