=9D he would have meant, like, renting out office space on Mars. Now he jus=
t means shrinking.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Someone probably could have built, like, =E2=
=80=9CWeWork but rational.=E2=80=9D Grow more slowly in the late 2010s, bec=
ome profitable, take a hit from Covid but survive by offering a product tha=
t is more appealing in a post-Covid world, but=C2=A0<em>less=C2=A0</em>of i=
t. My question is: Would you rather have built=C2=A0<em>that=C2=A0</em>prod=
