<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A while back, when the takeover battle for Scu=
lptor Capital Management Inc. was heating up, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.=
bloombergbusiness.com/click/33287990.258408/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmN=
vbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDgtMjMvY291bGQtc2N1bHB0b3ItYmUtYmV0dGVyLW=
