<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If I had told you, in 2021, that some combinat=
ion=C2=A0of (1) putting laser eyes on your Twitter profile picture and (2) =
then replacing your Twitter profile picture with a picture of a Bored Ape m=
ight cause you to go blind, you would have said things like =E2=80=9Cwhat=
=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Cno, you don=E2=80=99t understand, Twitter profile pi=
ctures are not real life, putting lasers in the eyes of your picture does n=
ot cause actual lasers to beam into your physical eyes and render you blind=
, this is a very elementary mistake.=E2=80=9D But you would have been wrong=
. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33287990.258408/=
aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGhldmVyZ2UuY29tLzIwMjMvMTEvNi8yMzk0ODQ2NC9ib3JlZC1hcGUtbmZ=
