" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-=
width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backg=
round-color: #ccc;"> Here is a thing</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Several people have reported experiencing eye =
pain, vision problems, and sunburnt skin on Sunday after attending ApeFest,=
 a Bored Ape Yacht Club NFT collection event in Hong Kong that ran from Nov=
ember 3rd-5th.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Some ApeFest attendees posted on X (formerly T=
witter) after seeking medical attention, with one person reporting that the=
y had been diagnosed with Photokeratitis =E2=80=94 aka, =E2=80=9Cwelder=E2=
=80=99s eye,=E2=80=9D a condition caused by unprotected exposure to ultravi=
olet radiation =E2=80=94 and another saying the issue was a result of UV fr=
om the stage lights, leading to speculation that the injuries were caused b=
y improper lighting used at the event.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Albert Burneko <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/33287990.258408/aHR0cHM6Ly9kZWZlY3Rvci5jb20vd2hlb=
i1ibGluZG5lc3MtaGl0cy1hLWh1bmRyZWQtYnVja3MtYS1zaGFyZS10aGVuLXdoby13aWxsLWJl=
