prop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color=
: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;"> writes</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is the sort of thing that hap=
pens to Homer Simpson. It happens to Master Shake. If you were reading a sa=
tirical novel and it mentioned a bunch of fanatical HODLers going blind at =
a festival for their dead worthless Ponzi-tech garbage because they stood t=
here like passive dullards and stared into a fly-by-night lasertag lighting=
 array equivalent to the sun while various sweaty Shingy-type guys ideated =
at them, you would snort-laugh and kinda roll your eyes and go, "Oh, come o=
n."</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I guess next month there will be a story=C2=A0=
about non-fungible token collectors at ApeFest <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33287990.258408/aHR0cHM6Ly9tYXNoYWJsZS5jb20vYX=
J0aWNsZS9tdWx0aXBsZS1zbHVycC1qdWljZXMtc2luZ2xlLWFwZS1tZW1lcw/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cBb6cf41b1" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> drinking slurp juice</a> and transforming in=
to mutant monkeys? Is it possible that the world is a simulation, and that =
crypto is somehow the nexus between the simulated world we experience and t=
he computer that runs it? If your Bored Ape dies, do you die in real life? =
Are NFTs=C2=A0<em>magic</em>? Probably not, no, probably someone just messe=
d up the lighting at ApeFest. Still, bizarre.</p>
